      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "cncf/toc",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "\u2696\ufe0f The CNCF Technical Oversight Committee (TOC) is the technical governing body of the CNCF Foundation."
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "cncf/toc",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "The CNCF TOC is the technical governing body of the CNCF. It admits and oversees all projects in the CNCF and has a mandate to facilitate driving neutral consensus for:"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "hashicorp/terraform",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Terraform enables you to safely and predictably create, change, and improve infrastructure. It is a source-available tool that codifies APIs into declarative configuration files that can be shared amongst team members, treated as code, edited, reviewed, and versioned."
